Services Offered: NEET Entrance Coaching , IIT Engineering Entrance Coaching , ISC Tuitions for 11th & 12th , SAT Coaching , Medical Entrance Coaching , NIFT/NID/CEED/FDDI Training , Chemistry Tuitions (11th & 12th) , Biology Tuitions (11th & 12th) , Advanced Level (A-Level) Maths Tuitions , Advanced Level (A-Level) Physics Tuitions , CBSE Tuitions for Physics , CBSE Tuitions for Chemistry , ICET Coaching , IIT HSEE Coaching , Advanced Level (A-Level) Chemistry Tuitions , CET Entrance Coaching , AIEEE Coaching , AIPMT Coaching , Architecture Entrance Coaching , JEE Advanced Coaching , CBSE Accounts (11th & 12th ) Tuitions , IIT-JEE Coaching ,
Details:
Since 1997, WE a group of academicians, IItians and entrepreneurs were successfully operating IIT-JEE, MHT-CET (PCM / PCB) entrance coaching in Nashik, Solapur & Latur under different brand names.
To improve our performance and standardizing our activities we were already toying with the idea of synchronizing our individual efforts under one umbrella. At the same time a group of academicians and entrepreneurs connected with IIT coaching in Pune approached for a joint collaboration. This was indeed a prudent idea and we moved on to come under one Brand and Umbrella. Soon with an ever energetic support from the like minded staff and faculties from Pune we formed a more professional and fresh coaching outfit the IIT PRATISHTHAN.
The worth and mettle of IIT Pratishthan was instantaneously understood and acknowledged by the educational stalwarts like, Deccan Education Societys Fergusson ACAR(Academy for Career Advancement & Research ), Pune, Maharashtra education Societys ACE (Academy for Career Excellence) in their Abasaheb Garware College Campus,Pune, by associating with us. There are other 30-35 leading schools in Pune & Maharashtra. Who have been closely associated with us for their counseling and competitive Exams information. Hope you agree that these above esteem institutes will only associate with the genuine and worthy Coaching institution.
We observed that Maharashtras IIT-JEE scene was bloated with false notion that IIT-JEE results are improving. Even last year we found out that more than 7000+ students migrated to coaching institutes in A.P, Delhi, Chennai and Kota. And those 5000 odd students who selected coaching institutions in Maharashtra had a different story to tell than actually projected.
Last year out of 5000 odd students took admissions with IIT-JEE aspiration, but ironically hardly 2% made it to the IITs. It clearly proves that compared to the national coaching standards this ratio was far below satisfaction.
We had no intentions of joining the band wagon but definitely looking forward to a different and a corrected approach to be adopted in coaching students from Maharashtra. We visited various institutions in India, observed the teaching patterns in Maharashtra, discussed with leading IIT faculties, brain stormed with previously excelled students and finally got a fresh coaching technique approved from the stalwarts of this industry which included Ex- dean, Professors, Research fellows and academicians from IITs and various college professors from across the state.

Details: FIITJEE  A synonym with quality education has brought a paradigm shift in the education sector of India. Founded in 1992 and evolved overtime as FIITJEE group, is considered as the most trustworthy brand and valued organisation by the Students, Parents and Teachers of the nation. FIITJEE has innovated new educational methodology and demonstrated extraordinary results in all targeted segments. FIITJEE has a proven track record of 23 plus years of excellence.FIITJEE, the trusted brand in the field of education, after escalating one by one milestone is in the mission of providing quality education to the students in India & abroad. To reduce the distance and to enable deserving students to reap benefits of FIITJEEs path breaking programs, FIITJEE now no longer limited to Delhi. It has opened its study centres in around 57 locations of India and a few abroad. None of these centres are franchises, as all its centres are FIITJEEs own centres and each run by academicians. In each centre same curriculum, same teaching methodology, same study material, same working system, same testing & monitoring mechanism is followed. FIITJEE Pune is one of those.PUNE being the city of young students & as rightly called as the OXFORD OF THE EAST deserves to have the best of the educational institutes of the world. It was one of the long cherished aspirations of the students & parents of Pune and the adjoining areas to have FIITJEE in Pune. Now students of Pune regions have the privilege to experience the unparalleled teaching methodology of the FIITJEE faculty members in their vicinity and to get the laurels they aspire for.In order to enable the students of Pune region to grab maximum number of results in All India Engineering entrance tests such as IITJEE (JEE Mains & Advance), BITSAT etc. FIITJEE started its operation in Pune since May 2010 with a handful of students & only three faculty members. Since then it was no looking back as each year we grew in number of students creating results both qualitative & quantitative yardstick in all most all competitive exams like IITJEE/KVPY/NTSE OLYMPIADS/NSTSE/ /State Scholarship exams etc. Presently FIITJEE Pune is having an enriched pool of 30 plus expert faculty members catering the academic needs of 800 plus students of standard IX  XII.In FIITJEE PUNE, we not only train students for academic excellence but also for their overall personality development, so they can be successful leaders in their chosen filed. FIITJEE PUNE is having two tied up Boys Hostels along with one hostel for the girls. Transport operators have mapped the entire Pune city by providing transport facility from almost all corners of the city to FIITJEE centre and the associated Schools & Hr. colleges, with their Mini Buses, Cabs & Vans. In FIITJEE Pune centre both Regular Week & Weekend batches options are available. Integrated education is provided in six associated schools (4 of CBSE & 2 of HSC) to impart stress free education towards the comprehensive preparation of competitive exams along with Boards.The mission has begun. The ray of hope is distinctly visible in the horizon. It is your turn to be part of the success story.Join early to take a lead over others

Tirupati Coaching Classes is now 16 years young.
Prof. Ashok Patil, the founder, principal of the classes aware of the humble beginning of Tirupati Coaching Classes in the year 1999 with just 10 students, is glad to have been able to expand the classes, to teach hundreds of students today, with more than 15 staff assisting him.
The bright performances of Tirupati Coaching Classes students year after year have been the driving force behind its success. The commitment of the teachers to draw the best out of   weak students has also been an important factor contributing to the trust the classes enjoys among the parents.
Apart from preparing students thoroughly for an outstanding performance at the exam, the classes also arranges guest lectures and seminars for the personality development of students. Lectures on Time Management, Stress Management, Study Skills, Career Guidance and achieving success have been found very useful by our students over the years.
The teachers of Tirupati Coaching Classes have periodical brain-storming sessions among themselves to plan their teaching method, monitor their own performances, gain Feed back from fellow members of the faculty and constantly think of providing more effective inputs to students to help them perform to their greatest potential.
Success is planned it is said. In addition to result oriented teaching , the classes conduct Test-series in a systematic manner before Board/University exams to equip the students with the right techniques they must follow to ensure an excellent performance in writing their answers at the Board/University exams.
Tirupati Coaching Classes strongly believes that the best is yet to come , and is always ready to reach higher levels of excellence in the years to come.

Details: Bodhee Academy was established in Pune in January 2015. People behind Bodhee Academy   Dr. N. Vyas:N. Vyas is an MSc in Biomedical Sciences from Delhi University and has done his PhD in from Germany. He has been awarded CSIR Junior Research Fellowship by Council of Scientific and Industrial Research (CSIR), Govt. of India. He was selected through a nationwide exam National Eligibility Test (NET), jointly conducted by CSIR and UGC in 2009 with all India Rank 24th. He has received call for prestigious Shayama Prasad Mukerjee award three times which is given to top thirty Masters students of India. He was awarded CSIR Catch them young Fellowship from Council of Scientific and Industrial Research (CSIR), Govt. of India in 2009 and 2010.   Brijesh Pandey:By qualification, he is an electronics engineer; by profession, he is a verbal aptitude trainer. He had consistently scored 99 plus percentile in the verbal section when CAT (Common Admission Test) was in the paper-pencil format. Apart from teaching verbal aptitude, he also designs questions on a variety of topics; most of the questions displayed on this website have been designed by him; being fond of movies, books and documentaries, he often suggests unique and interesting ways by which students can develop their knowledge about myriads of things.   Rakesh Vishwakarma:An IT (Information Technology) engineer from NIT, Raipur and an MBA from Department of Pune University, Rakesh has been a quantitative aptitude trainer for the past 9 years and has worked with organizations such as PT and Career Launcher; he has the knack of teaching multiple concepts through just one question; many of the questions on this website have been designed by him; he has been getting 99 plus percentile in the CAT (Common Admission Test) for the past four years and has been getting calls from the prestigious IIMs. Apart from teaching quantitative aptitude, he is very fond of coding and programming.We help students in choosing the right research area and provide guidance onresearch opportunities in universities in Europe and USA.

Indira School of Communication, established in 2004, is part of Shree Chanakya Education Societys Indira Group of Institutes (established 1994). Under the visionary leadership of Dr. Tarita Shankar.The Indira School of Communication is a front rank media school that bears a unique blend of academic and innovative practices. Established in 2004, under the prestigious Indira Group of Institutes of the Shree Chanakya Education Society, Pune, Indira School of Communication has come a long way from its modest beginnings. The institute is among the finest media schools of the country today and has been adjudged the best media school twice consecutively.

VisionIndira School of Communication is the instrument of a vision to create a platform of excellence that will help progress the standards in the professions of news, radio/television software, advertising, public relations, journalism and media management.
MissionIndira School of Communication promotes innovative and independent thinking among our trainees through a forward-looking academic system that provides theoretical, research and practical input.
GoalIndira School of Communication aims at all-round growth of its trainees through various academic and managerial concepts. Continuous evaluation, de-emphasized examinations, social development projects, fitness activities (gym, yoga, aerobics), and plenty of practical and real-world exposure.

Name: CFA® Exam Preparation & Coaching Classes Tutorials by ProCore
Services Offered: Chartered Financial Analyst (CFA) Coaching ,
Details: ProCore, a venture founded by IIT Alumni, provides coaching in various professional courses like CFA (Level 1, level 2, level 3), FRM etc in India. ProCore provides coaching classes in Delhi, Mumbai, Pune, Kolkata, Hyderabad, Chennai and Bangalore. The International CFA course has become very popular in India and the CFA candidates and charter holders enjoy several benefits. The CFA charter is well respected and appreciated in the global investment community. CFA education ensures that the charter holder has comprehensive knowledge and fundamental understanding of the financial markets. The course content is global in nature and is rightly sought after by candidates all over the world. Growing acceptance of this qualification in the country as indicated by the surge in demand for the services of CFA candidates and charter holders by various employers in the investment banking and financial companies. The prestige of the charter in the professional investment community can be attributed to the challenging nature of the examination in each level. Thus a need for a systematic and comprehensive program is necessary for candidates who have registered for the CFA exams. The ProCore program highlights are as follows: ProCore provides CFA classes lasting over 100 hours that aid in your preparation and add significant value to understanding of the CFA exam curriculum. These CFA classes will cover the entire syllabus of level one, level two and level three for the corresponding students and ensure conceptual understanding through practical examples, periodic tests and mock exams in order to equip them with requisite skills to pass the CFA exam. Along with the classes, CFA notes of each level are provided by ProCore to the corresponding students. These notes contain the concepts of the course and the unique examples discussed in the classes. The faculty on board with ProCore that provides the CFA training comprises of CFA Level 3 subject expert professionals who have minimum 3 yrs experience in the financial services field. Our teaching methodology ensures that the students develop a firm understanding of the concepts through current practical examples based on their experience in the industry that are not found in any CFA textbooks.
